ight not be included in future versions of simuPOP. For example, if you have implemented a particular mating scheme for certain animal populations, it might be a good idea to add it to this module so that it can be distributed with simuPOP. Note that backward compatibility is not guaranteed for this module so scripts that make use of this module might be locked to a particular version of simuPOP.%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a
